            paragraph2: 'TSH-160 solid waste shredder equipped with Siemens PLC-based advanced automation system offers SCADA integration, remote intervention, predictive maintenance and IoT connectivity infrastructure. With 1600 mm extra long rotor, 64 special alloy hardened steel blades and reinforced gearbox, it provides maximum torque and durability. Thanks to the dual motor system, it guarantees uninterrupted operation even under heavy loads in plastic shredding machine and recycling crusher applications. Operates safely with high torque and low speed combination.',
            paragraph3: 'MT Makina TSH-160 single shaft shredder is designed for large-scale recycling complexes, automotive recovery centers, municipal waste management facilities, industrial zone joint waste processing centers and port-customs waste processing. Can be integrated with fully automatic conveyor feeding, magnetic separator, air separator, discharge screws and bale press. Offers fast return on investment with low unit cost and high durability in terms of solid waste shredder prices.',
            paragraph4: 'With single shaft shredder technology, TSH-160 provides extraordinary results in plastic scrap crusher, bale shredder, rubber shredder and scrap tire shredder applications. Optimized cutter geometry with long rotor and wide screen surface provides homogeneous shredding and energy efficiency. Delivers reliable performance even in harsh conditions thanks to powerful drive motors and durable cutting tools. Offers economic advantage in mega capacity projects in plastic crusher prices.',
            paragraph5: 'TSH-160 single shaft solid waste shredder minimizes operating costs with energy-efficient special blade design and intelligent load management. It is an ideal investment for metropolitan municipality integrated waste management projects, large industrial parks and free zone waste processing centers. Requires minimum maintenance with automatic lubrication system, industrial cooling system and solid steel body. Supported by European safety standards, CE certification and 3-year warranty.',
            paragraph6: 'Providing sustainability in waste management, TSH-160 offers high efficiency, environmental benefits and economic advantages to businesses by optimizing recycling processes. As Turkey\'s leading shredder manufacturer MT Makina, we offer single shaft solid waste shredder price quotes, turnkey project solutions and 24/7 technical support. Contact our professional consultancy team for your plastic shredder, fabric shredder, pallet shredder and paper shredder needs. TSH-160 is the recommended top-grade shredding solution for heavy industrial applications and high capacity recycling projects.'
